data.description: Experience living in Fossil Lake Ranch, one of the most sought-after subdivisions in Fort Collins and Loveland! This meticulously designed 5-bedroom, 2.5-bath KEM home offers unparalleled style and comfort. With oak hardwood floors throughout the main level, a gourmet kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and ample cabinet and counter space, tons of natural lighting throughout, and an unfinished basement waiting for your personal design, 3627 Wild View Drive offers exceptional living in an extraordinary location. Enjoying walking-distance proximity to the the best elementary/middle/high school progression in Poudre School District, a few minutes' drive to Colorado's top charter schools, and easy access to Twin Silos Park and some of Fort Collins' other best outdoor opportunities, this home can't be beat as a family-friendly location. Physicians and parents alike will appreciate how close 3627 Wild View Drive is to northern Colorado's best hospitals. IT professionals will love that Intel, Broadcom, HPE, HP, and other global companies are within walking distance of home. And after work, come home to relax in front of a cozy fire in the main living area or outside in one of the subdivision's largest and best-kept backyards. Don't miss the chance to make this dream home yours! Schedule your showing today.
